# Root marker for environment configuration.
#
# Real environment files live next to the code that consumes them and are
# git-ignored. Copy the matching example and fill in local values:
#
#   infra/.env.example     -> infra/.env       (docker compose: postgres, livekit, egress, api)
#   apps/api/.env.example  -> apps/api/.env     (host-side Prisma + local API dev)
#   apps/web/.env.example  -> apps/web/.env     (Vite dev server)
#
# No secret is ever committed. Tokens and passwords are read from env only.
